---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Team - Inform Growth"
  description="Built by two people who experienced the same failure mode from opposite sides. Meet the founders of Inform Growth."
>
  <!-- Section 1: The Origin -->
  <section class="origin-section section geo-grid">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="origin-content fade-up">
        <h1>Built by two people who experienced the same failure mode from opposite sides.</h1>
        <div class="origin-story">
          <p>
            Jaron built revenue systems for scaling companies and watched sales reps route around the very CRMs he built. The processes were clean on paper. The data architecture was sound. But the tools went unused because they were designed without understanding how deals actually close.
          </p>
          <p>
            Joseph closed enterprise deals and watched RevOps consultants design processes that ignored how sales actually work. The pipeline reports looked great in board meetings. But the forecasts were fiction because the systems underneath were built by people who'd never carried a quota.
          </p>
          <p class="origin-conclusion">
            <strong>Inform Growth is their answer:</strong> revenue infrastructure designed by the people who have to live with it. A systems architect and a sales closer, working together on every engagement.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Section 2: Founder Profiles -->
  <section class="profiles-section section bg-light">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="text-center fade-up">The Founders</h2>

      <div class="founders-grid fade-up">
        <!-- Jaron Sander -->
        <div class="founder-profile">
          <div class="founder-header">
            <div class="founder-avatar">
              <span>JS</span>
            </div>
            <div class="founder-title">
              <h3>Jaron Sander</h3>
              <p class="founder-role">Co-Founder / Revenue Systems Architect</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <p class="founder-bio">
            Builds the systems that make revenue predictable. Player-coach model - still in the code, still on client calls. Started as a one-person RevOps team and learned that the best systems are the ones people actually use.
          </p>

          <div class="founder-metrics">
            <div class="metric">
              <span class="metric-value">400K+</span>
              <span class="metric-label">Records Migrated</span>
            </div>
            <div class="metric">
              <span class="metric-value">75%</span>
              <span class="metric-label">CRM Cost Reduction</span>
            </div>
            <div class="metric">
              <span class="metric-value">40%</span>
              <span class="metric-label">Churn Reduction</span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="founder-credentials">
            <h4>Credentials</h4>
            <ul>
              <li>Led RevOps for 3x scaling SaaS companies</li>
              <li>Consolidated 7 CRMs into unified architecture</li>
              <li>Built custom integrations across HubSpot, Salesforce, and Segment</li>
              <li>Designed data architectures serving 3M+ contacts</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="founder-tools">
            <h4>Core Tools</h4>
            <p>HubSpot, Salesforce, Segment, Python, SQL, Make, n8n, Custom APIs</p>
          </div>

          <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/jaron-sander" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="founder-linkedin">
            Connect on LinkedIn →
          </a>
        </div>

        <!-- Joseph Anthony -->
        <div class="founder-profile">
          <div class="founder-header">
            <div class="founder-avatar">
              <span>JA</span>
            </div>
            <div class="founder-title">
              <h3>Joseph Anthony</h3>
              <p class="founder-role">Co-Founder / Enterprise Sales</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <p class="founder-bio">
            Closes the deals that prove the systems work. Learned at Checkout.com and Ivey Business School that sales tools only matter if sellers can actually sell with them. The systems architect's built-in stress test.
          </p>

          <div class="founder-metrics">
            <div class="metric">
              <span class="metric-value">$900K</span>
              <span class="metric-label">Largest Deal Closed</span>
            </div>
            <div class="metric">
              <span class="metric-value">$2M</span>
              <span class="metric-label">New Business (4 mo)</span>
            </div>
            <div class="metric">
              <span class="metric-value">70%</span>
              <span class="metric-label">Revenue Growth</span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="founder-credentials">
            <h4>Credentials</h4>
            <ul>
              <li>Enterprise Account Executive at Checkout.com</li>
              <li>Ivey Business School (HBA)</li>
              <li>$110K non-dilutive funding secured</li>
              <li>Built outbound engines from zero pipeline</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="founder-tools">
            <h4>Core Tools</h4>
            <p>HubSpot Sales Hub, Gong, Outreach, LinkedIn Sales Navigator, Notion</p>
          </div>

          <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/josephanthony" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="founder-linkedin">
            Connect on LinkedIn →
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Section 3: Why We Work This Way -->
  <section class="why-section section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="text-center fade-up">Why We Work This Way</h2>

      <div class="why-grid fade-up">
        <div class="why-card">
          <div class="why-number">1</div>
          <h3>The Problem We Kept Seeing</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>RevOps strategy handed off to someone else for implementation</li>
            <li>Sales process designed by people who've never closed a deal</li>
            <li>Data architecture built without understanding how reps actually work</li>
            <li>Consultants who diagnose but don't fix</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="why-card">
          <div class="why-number">2</div>
          <h3>What We Built Instead</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Zero-handoff model - one team from diagnosis to delivery</li>
            <li>Sales architect + systems architect on every engagement</li>
            <li>The person who finds the problem fixes it</li>
            <li>No discovery phases that lead to more discovery phases</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="why-card">
          <div class="why-number">3</div>
          <h3>What It Means for You</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>The person who finds the problem fixes it</li>
            <li>The system gets used because it was designed by someone who sells with it</li>
            <li>Faster time to value - no translation between strategists and implementers</li>
            <li>Accountability that doesn't end at the deck</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Section 4: CTA -->
  <section class="team-cta section geo-grid">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="cta-content fade-up">
        <h2>Let's find what your revenue engine is leaking.</h2>
        <p class="cta-sub">30 minutes. We map the gaps - Sales, Data, and Systems. No pitch before you see the diagnosis.</p>
        <div class="cta-buttons">
          <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary btn-large">Book Your Deep-Scan</a>
          <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-secondary">Just want to talk first →</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  /* Section 1: Origin */
  .origin-section {
    background-color: var(--navy);
    padding: var(--space-section) 0;
  }

  .origin-content {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .origin-section h1 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-h1);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--white);
    line-height: 1.15;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-8);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .origin-story {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-6);
  }

  .origin-story p {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    color: var(--off-white);
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .origin-conclusion {
    padding: var(--space-6);
    background-color: rgba(200, 240, 74, 0.1);
    border-left: 4px solid var(--sky-blue);
    border-radius: var(--card-radius);
  }

  .origin-conclusion strong {
    color: var(--sky-blue);
  }

  /* Section 2: Profiles */
  .profiles-section h2 {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-2xl);
  }

  .founders-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-8);
  }

  @media (min-width: 900px) {
    .founders-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }
  }

  .founder-profile {
    background-color: var(--card-bg);
    border-radius: var(--card-radius);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-card);
    padding: var(--space-7);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-6);
  }

  .founder-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-4);
  }

  .founder-avatar {
    width: 80px;
    height: 80px;
    background-color: var(--navy);
    border-radius: 8px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .founder-avatar span {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-xl);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--sky-blue);
  }

  .founder-title h3 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-xl);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--heading-color);
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-1);
  }

  .founder-role {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--text-caption);
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--sky-blue);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .founder-bio {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--muted-text);
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .founder-metrics {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: var(--space-4);
    padding: var(--space-6);
    background-color: var(--pale-blue);
    border-radius: var(--card-radius);
  }

  .metric {
    text-align: center;
  }

  .metric-value {
    display: block;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-xl);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--navy);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-1);
  }

  .metric-label {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--text-caption);
    color: var(--slate);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.03em;
  }

  .founder-credentials h4,
  .founder-tools h4 {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--text-caption);
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--sky-blue);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-3);
  }

  .founder-credentials ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-2);
  }

  .founder-credentials li {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--muted-text);
    padding-left: var(--space-6);
    position: relative;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .founder-credentials li::before {
    content: '✓';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--emerald);
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .founder-tools p {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--muted-text);
    margin: 0;
  }

  .founder-linkedin {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--sky-blue);
    transition: color var(--transition-fast);
    margin-top: auto;
  }

  .founder-linkedin:hover {
    color: var(--sky-blue-light);
  }

  /* Section 3: Why We Work This Way */
  .why-section {
    background-color: var(--page-bg);
  }

  .why-section h2 {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-2xl);
  }

  .why-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-8);
  }

  @media (min-width: 900px) {
    .why-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    }
  }

  .why-card {
    background-color: var(--card-bg);
    border-radius: var(--card-radius);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-card);
    padding: var(--space-7);
  }

  .why-number {
    width: 48px;
    height: 48px;
    background-color: var(--sky-blue);
    color: var(--white);
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    font-weight: 700;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    border-radius: 8px;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
  }

  .why-card h3 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--heading-color);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
  }

  .why-card ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-3);
  }

  .why-card li {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--muted-text);
    padding-left: var(--space-6);
    position: relative;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .why-card li::before {
    content: '→';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--sky-blue);
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  /* Section 4: CTA */
  .team-cta {
    background-color: var(--navy);
  }

  .cta-content {
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .team-cta h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-h2);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--white);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-6);
  }

  .cta-sub {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    color: var(--off-white);
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-8);
  }

  .cta-buttons {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-4);
  }

  @media (min-width: 600px) {
    .cta-buttons {
      flex-direction: row;
      justify-content: center;
    }
  }

  .btn-large {
    padding: 16px 32px;
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
  }

  /* Scroll animations */
  .fade-up {
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateY(20px);
    transition: opacity 0.4s ease, transform 0.4s ease;
  }

  .fade-up.visible {
    opacity: 1;
    transform: translateY(0);
  }
</style>

<script>
  // Scroll-triggered fade-up animations
  document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', () => {
    const fadeElements = document.querySelectorAll('.fade-up');

    const observer = new IntersectionObserver((entries) => {
      entries.forEach(entry => {
        if (entry.isIntersecting) {
          entry.target.classList.add('visible');
        }
      });
    }, {
      threshold: 0.1,
      rootMargin: '0px 0px -50px 0px'
    });

    fadeElements.forEach(el => observer.observe(el));
  });
</script>
